node.text:
I am voting for Joe because I want to raise my son in a decent world, and Joe Biden is a decent man. He respects the military. He respects scientists. He respect women, and a woman’s right to choose. He respect equality for all. He respects Black Lives Matter. He thinks big, rich companies should pay more taxes.. He is worried about the environment for generations to come. He is a leader who will take a shot at ending Covid.

I’m sick of being lied to. I’m sick of temper tantrums and pitting people against each other.  I don’t care if you’re a Republican or Democrat, we all live here.  There was a time when we didn’t blame someone or the "other side" for every problem.  I’m sick of disrespecting women, and minorities, and people from other countries.. I’m sick of not listening to experts...and being rude to people with differing opinions.  I am sick of making shit up constantly. And inciting violence.  I am sick of using our government and taxpayer dollars to fund a maniac who just watches tv, golfs and furthers his self interests. We are a laughingstock of the world.  World leaders laugh right at our President's face, even the dictators he sucks up to. Even the people he employs, who each one quit and renounce him. Did you ever think you would see that day? Did you ever think we would live with someone in power who renounces the foundations of Democracy? He does it every day.

I know i’m the reality TV guy, so who cares what I think. And I’m just sharing here. And reality TV is great entertainment, but this is real life - and he is like a lunatic one-season Housewife (who would've been fired from the show) who has access to the nukes. 

I am voting for Joe Biden.

node.title: I’m Proudly Voting For Joe Biden

#ad You know I love a good summer margarita. That is why I challenged @courteneycoxofficial
and @daveeddiggs to The Ultimate Margarita Showdown with @cointreau_us @archdigest.
Watch our face-off and vote for the best margarita (mine of course) - it’s for a good cause!
#MargaritaShowdown
- 1oz Cointreau
- 2oz Blanco Tequila
- 1/2oz fresh lime juice
- 2 passionfruits (flesh & seeds)
- 6 basil leaves
- Rim glass with salt

Shake with ice & enjoy!

archdigest.com/margaritaseason
